# zget UI Polish & Architectural Review

## Summary

Completed a comprehensive UI polish for the Regions tab and delivered a full architectural review with 2026 technology trend recommendations.

---

## Regions Tab UI Fix

### Problem
- Category chips lacked hover feedback and visual polish
- Sections appeared "smooshed" with insufficient spacing
- Inline styles made maintenance difficult

### Solution
Added CSS classes for:
- `.category-chip` with hover effects (lift + shadow)
- `.region-summary` with better spacing
- `.region-chips` container (gap: 10px, margin-bottom: 24px)
- `.site-row` with hover animation (border highlight + slide effect)

