## Architectural Review Summary

| Rating | Category |
|--------|----------|
| ✅ Strong | Tech stack (FastAPI + SQLite + Vanilla JS) |
| ✅ Strong | MCP integration (ahead of its time) |
| ✅ Strong | H.264 standard enforcement |
| ⚠️ Gap | No Service Worker (incomplete PWA) |
| ⚠️ Gap | Monolithic frontend (1,281 lines) |
| ⚠️ Gap | Blocking database calls in async context |

### Prioritized Recommendations
1. 🔴 **Service Worker + Offline Mode** — core PWA feature
2. 🔴 **Async Database Migration** — performance
3. 🟡 **Component-Based Frontend** — maintainability
4. 🟢 **Librarian VLM Integration** — differentiator

